<p>的<a class="route-link nolebase-route-link-invalid" href="#" target="_target">关系</a>，其中 <span v-pre="" class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span></span></span></span> 是<a class="route-link nolebase-route-link-invalid" href="#" target="_target">多元函数</a>。</p>
